name: Zhuge Ling
skill: Increases the DMG taken by 2 random enemies by (48%/59%) for a limited time.
ability: Moderately increases all allies' critical damage.

additional_data.description: The spirit of the sister of a famous military tactician from the Three Kingdoms period in Chinese history. She has a complex about the fact that her name didn't go down in history even though she worked just as hard as her brother and is just as smart. Since becoming a spirit, she's been doing everything she can to make a name for herself.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Increase battle time limit during the "Outbreak! A Day of Battle in Shinjuku!" event.
◦ Summon rate increased until 03/08/16

main: "I'm just as much a genius as my brother!"
skill: "I've got you in the palm of my hand."
summon: "My brother this, my brother that-- pssht! I can fight on my own, thank you!"
limit_break: "At my current level, I could knock him out with one punch!"
